        <description>A decal is one way of using images. We&amp;rsquo;ll create a very rough layout by hand in Inkscape
 Shot layout Create a shot layout in Scalable Vector Graphics  Open a blueprint that was exported from Visual Pinball into Inkscape (not import) Keep the file dimensions when it asks Create bezier lines on a seperate layer for shot angles When happy hide the Blueprint layer Export the image as Page, checking the dimensions are in px and were the same dimesions as the blueprint.</description>
        
